{"tid":1887893,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（吹大雞，要超過2萬投訴信）一人一信反攻投訴警訊佢老母","createTime":"2020-02-20T00:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T13:54:04.000Z","uid":72431,"like":35,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"43b9530ef8b8af81e540ed0618f7229904fd7f50","tid":1887893,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00:48:08.000Z","msg":"事緣商經局：收到200多個涉及《頭條新聞》投訴<br />\n <br />\n佢要計投訴數字，就同佢玩，同佢鬥多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n[size=5]Template 已有，禁個制就投訴到，無成本，連登仔唔係咁都懶嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">to<br />\nwebmaster@ofca.gov.hk，<br />\nceo@ceo.gov.hk，sced@cedb.gov.hk， pscci@cedb.gov.hk，ccu@rthk.hk,kwleung@rthk.hk，<br />\nccibenq@cedb.gov.hk ，kwleung@rthk.hk，<br />\nsio-newsroom-pprb@police.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTitle:對香港電台電視部製作的節目&lt;警訊&gt;作嚴正投訴<br />\n<br />\n致 通訊事務管理局辦公室及各相關部門，<br />\n<br />\n本人現希望向貴局對香港電台電視部製作的節目&lt;警訊&gt;作嚴正投訴。<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，警方的民望為眾政府部門之末，這個節目的製作實為浪費公帑,並為個別部門建立良好形象，與事實警方形象不符，實為粉飾櫥窗之舉。<br />\n<br />\n眾多部門不應只有警方獨有宣傳平台，若要提供教育資訊，請問難道消防局，衞生局不應個別製作《消防訊》或《衛生抗疫》等相關節目為市民提供滅火，衛生知識？更何況在這武漢肺炎橫行時代，政府沒有一個節目為市民提供必要的抗疫資訊，實令市民失望。<br />\n<br />\n而事實上，&lt;警訊&gt;一向內容偏頗，不能反映警方真實形象。相反，警訊應花更大篇幅講述當年轟動一時警署強姦案的案發經過，製作案件重演單元，讓市民了解案件始末，提高警覺。另外，亦可訪問其他警員了解他們心理發展，探討休班警員犯罪率偏高的原因。<br />\n<br />\n本人現要求透過貴局，對&lt;警訊&gt;作嚴正投訴，表達我對節目的高度不滿。同時亦希望貴局會根據&lt;警訊&gt;的不受歡迎程度，停止有關節目製作。<br />\n<br />\n煩請貴局通知香港電台後賜予回覆。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝<br />\n<br />\nYour name </span>"},{"pid":"9fc5f003bd4f53b471fd2eceb10ca76d6b2ab43f","tid":1887893,"uid":178440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00:52:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"faa7a0134b59395636653dc6bcd5803949eee975","tid":1887893,"uid":40766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00:55:05.000Z","msg":"Push."},{"pid":"27c4fd3e4f8742334088e1ce520fc8771e045067","tid":1887893,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00:57:00.000Z","msg":"當香港人仲掛住排口罩 搶廁紙 討論邊個邊個ig女神<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1887691\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1887691</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推下啊唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d0fc5b9200e97576fc910d9bcc07dd56ed698a","tid":1887893,"uid":40766,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00:57:52.000Z","msg":"webmaster@ofca.gov.hk, <br />\nceo@ceo.gov.hk, sced@cedb.gov.hk, pscci@cedb.gov.hk, ccu@rthk.hk, kwleung@rthk.hk, <br />\nccibenq@cedb.gov.hk, kwleung@rthk.hk,<br />\nsio-newsroom-pprb@police.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n畀你啲全形逗號玩撚死。"},{"pid":"b83e9a7d3fdfa4c6be3b3dc86df0913940fae23e","tid":1887893,"uid":190537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:04:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7784669424bc6ab85664c83cc42986f605f349ee","tid":1887893,"uid":264887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:06:28.000Z","msg":"識玩，即做"},{"pid":"0c25503b5caa07743c3c09c3d4201b16948b1655","tid":1887893,"uid":96871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:09:59.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n冇損失既野都唔做咪撚話自己黃"},{"pid":"cf2feee518e7da8efa164a958f69746c96b942ef","tid":1887893,"uid":225117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f56101c2d27f3338fae02f4d863aa9b8651d4b","tid":1887893,"uid":34986,